{"product_id":"green-ajmeri-attar-roll-on-6ml-al-saalim-perfumers-alcohol-free","title":"Green Ajmeri Attar (Roll-On 6ml) | Al-Saalim Perfumers | Alcohol-Free","description":"\u003cp\u003e Enjoy the fresh, herbal, and soothing fragrance of Green Ajmeri Attar by Al-Saalim Perfumers.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis attar is known for its green, earthy, and calming aroma that helps relax the mind and provides a refreshing feel.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eGreen Ajmeri is a traditional fragrance that is especially suitable for prayers, daily wear, and warm weather.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIts alcohol-free formula is skin-friendly and maintains a natural fragrance that lasts for long hours.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eKey Features\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFragrance Type: Green, Herbal \u0026amp; Fresh\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eQuantity: 6 ml Roll-On\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAlcohol-Free\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLong-lasting and refreshing fragrance\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePremium glass roll-on bottle\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSuitable for both men and women\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhy Choose Green Ajmeri\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFresh and natural herbal fragrance\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eProvides a calm and peaceful feel\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePerfect for daily use and prayers\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eElegant packaging, suitable for gifting\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHow to Use\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eApply a small amount on your neck, wrists, or pulse points and experience pure freshness throughout the day.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"AL-SAALIM PERFUMES","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50472867201271,"sku":null,"price":179.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0923\/0755\/4551\/files\/B6AE23D4-9323-41D9-9238-F641430A564A.png?v=1777870289","url":"https:\/\/alsaalimperfume.shop\/products\/green-ajmeri-attar-roll-on-6ml-al-saalim-perfumers-alcohol